Neiman Marcus Group LTD LLC: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 27, 2017 4:30 AM ET
Specialty Retail

Company Overview of Neiman Marcus Group LTD LLC



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Neiman Marcus Group LTD LLC offers fashion products retailing services. The company was founded in 2013 and is based in Dallas, Texas. Neiman Marcus Group LTD LLC operates as a subsidiary of Neiman Marcus Group, Inc.


1618 Main StreetOne Marcus SquareDallas, TX 75201United StatesFounded in 2013



Phone: 214-743-7600








